  <div>
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-wine-700 mb-2">How many bottles of wine should I buy for Thanksgiving dinner?</h3>
    <p class="text-gray-700">Plan for one bottle per every two to three guests, assuming a 4-hour celebration with appetizers and dinner. For a table of 8, purchase 3-4 bottles, ensuring you have both red and white options. Consider buying an extra bottle of your crowd-favorite since Thanksgiving wines often get opened for seconds, and having a backup prevents mid-meal disappointment.</p>
