  <div>
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-wine-700 mb-2">Can I serve sparkling wine throughout the entire Thanksgiving meal?</h3>
    <p class="text-gray-700">Absolutely! Sparkling wine is one of the most versatile Thanksgiving choices, with its bubbles and acidity cutting through rich gravies while cleansing the palate between bites. Champagne, Cava, or American sparkling wines work beautifully from appetizers through dessert. The effervescence also adds a celebratory touch that matches the holiday's festive spirit.</p>
